Fales Library Collection of Artwork and Memorabilia

The Fales Library Collection of Artwork and Memorabilia was created in 2017 to track artworks that had been found in the collection and artworks donated to the Fales Library & Special Collections. The collection consists of artworks found in the collection and artworks donated to the Fales Library & Special Collections. The artworks consist of paintings, drawings, photographs, religious objects, realia, and sculptures. The artworks date from 1851 to 2016.
